postcontent:
For sale is a Sig Pro SP2009 BMS in 9mm. The BMS is a special edition made by Sig with a slide mounted safety. This is very rare as Sig hasn't offered this option except for this model. The story goes that Sig was in contract to produce this gun for a South American government and the contract fell through so instead of destroying the slides, they sold them in the US market. Searching online yields limited results, but you can find the story and see how rare they are. Included with the Sig is the original magazine plus 4 additional mags (all factory Sig magazines), two grip sizes (bigger one is installed), an Uncle Mike's IWB nylon holster (not shown), gun lock and original blue Sig Sauer case.
